url|https://www.buzzfeed.com/alvinzhou/this-easy-chocolate-chip-cookie-dough-is-great-for-food-prep?bffbtasty&amp;ref=bffbtasty&amp;utm_term=.fu7ev2EKg#.fi6GKmJQe
